{"type": "article", "id": 5450, "title": "Cheetah 电动折叠自行车", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-22T07:29:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233903n8oQJbBpfsPhMFzH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t市面上那些动辄上万元的高性能电动自行车是不是苦于荷包紧张买不下手？日前，来自澳大利亚的 Dillenger 公司推出了一款名为「Cheetah」的电动折叠自行车，采用新型生产工艺，降低了产品的造价。Cheetah 车身重量仅为 28 千克，其巧妙的折叠设计非常便于携带。此外，Cheetah 还配备了一款可以拆卸更换的 12Ah 24V 电池，时速可达 45 km，如果采用踏板助力装置的话，时速也能达到 20 km。定价 399 澳元（约合人民币 2038 元），<a href=\"http://dillenger.com.au/product-category/electric-bikes/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODc2NDg1NTE2\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233900UsaIxAw2MCnz8qcY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052339011WwfJ9iQ6kSloPF7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052339022fmIQsyPNAEubqWM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233902cUiECMHsNlGdpyFk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.753125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233903tuOJfPeaEj9gyCUW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}